Y fallback keeps installed agents instead of falling back to detection\\n\\n---\\n\\n### 8. Code Architecture\\n\\n**Key files:**\\n- `/Users/dip/Repositories/cli/cmd/entire/cli/setup.go` - Main enable/disable commands (1347 lines)\\n- `/Users/dip/Repositories/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/claudecode/hooks.go` - Agent hook installation\\n- `/Users/dip/Repositories/cli/cmd/entire/cli/config.go` - `GetAgentsWithHooksInstalled()`\\n- `/Users/dip/Repositories/cli/cmd/entire/cli/agent/registry.go` - Agent registry and detection\\n- `/Users/dip/Repositories/cli/cmd/entire/cli/settings/settings.go` - Settings persistence\\n\\n**Test coverage:**\\n- `setup_test.go` has comprehensive tests for agent selection scenarios:\\n  - `TestDetectOrSelectAgent_ReRun_AlwaysPromptsWithInstalledPreSelected` (line 1173)\\n  - `TestUninstallDeselectedAgentHooks_MultipleInstalled_DeselectOne` (line 1301)\\n  - Tests verify hooks are correctly detected, installed, and uninstalled\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Summary\\n\\nThe `entire enable` command uses a **multi-layered approach** for agent management:\\n\\n1. **Detection**: Via agent-specific `DetectPresence()` checking for config directories\\n2. **Pre-selection**: Combines installed hooks + newly detected agents on re-run\\n3. **Installation**: Per-agent hook installation with idempotency checks\\n4. **Uninstallation**: Removes hooks for deselected agents during re-run\\n5. **Persistence**: Agent hooks in agent config files (`.claude/settings.json`), Entire config in `.entire/settings.json`\\n6. **Re-run awareness**: Always prompts on re-run, pre-selects installed agents, enables deselection with cleanup\"},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"agentId: a8bca54 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\\n<usage>total_tokens: 78494\\ntool_uses: 35\\nduration_ms: 96156</usage>\"}]}]},\"uuid\":\"4d675de0-3da7-4725-9dd1-51913f851228\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-20T11:37:59.961Z\",\"toolUseResult\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"prompt\":\"Investigate the `en